data.title: Kinnikinnick Brand Kickapoo Joy-Juice by Williams, Jonathan: Near fine Hardcover (2004) Limited Edition., Signed by Author(s)
data.meta_description: Signed by Author(s) - Limited Edition. - Hardcover - Turkey Press, Isla Vista - 2004 - Condition: Near fine - Long 8vo. Later limited edition bound by hand at the Turkey Press studio in sewn-boards covered with white and terracotta paper handmade from raw flax cooked in lime at the University of Iowa Center for the book, Oakdale Campus Paper Facility. 145 press numbered copies signedby both the poet and the artist of which this is #76. Additionally laid in a single page with #76 and proof written on it in pencil. A near fine copy with faint foxing along textblock. - Kinnikinnick Brand Kickapoo Joy-Juice
